<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> wir <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> worten <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>, daz
                        ewr kriege nu zu gut <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn, des seyn wir fro
                        und haben das <expan>sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gern
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn von
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> ladung <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> haben
